# Performance and a11y

- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` (see `tokens.css`).
- Lazy-load 3D and heavy modals in later phases.
- Use shadcn for dialogs/sheets/forms (focus management).
- Landmarks: `header`, `main`, `footer`, `section` with labels where needed.
- Tree-shake: import shadcn components from their file paths, not barrel re-exports of entire library.
